{"tid":2225957,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"荔景邨單位起火濃煙沖天 逾百居民疏散","createTime":"2020-10-01T16:36:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-01T16:54:31.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b221251a7e7151368dd9bf65e253491b843de26d","tid":2225957,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T16:36:00.000Z","msg":"葵涌晚上發生大火。晚上11時，荔景邨仰景樓中層一單位發生火警，冒出大量濃煙，火舌噴出窗外，火焰更波及毗鄰及樓上單位，多人報警求助，有居民需要疏散到大廈對開空地位置。據現場消息指，起火單位內有一名男子被困，消防正在現場開喉灌救，暫時未知起火原因。<br />\n<br />\n讀者梁先生指現場火勢非常猛烈，外牆被嚴重熏黑，火舌不停從窗口竄出，現場未有傳爆炸聲，但有過百居民疏散至空地位置逃生。<br />\n<br />\n當區區議員王天仁表示，起火單位為8樓一單位，火勢至晚上11時半左右受控，但單位仍不斷冒出濃煙，大批消防在場戒備，向單位射水降溫及派員入大廈內搜救。有街坊向他透露，單位內居住的是一名獨居人士，但身份未明。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201001/4BOHBWCX6BA43HWADHBREBH674/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201001%2F4BOHBWCX6BA43HWADHBREBH674%2F&d=2MheXYw%2FBwPqfvV%2BE34w1z8W653rZVWOX%2F4zqp%2BjK3Y%3D&h=d463027a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201001%2F4BOHBWCX6BA43HWADHBREBH674%2F&h=87c80bba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201001/4BOHBWCX6BA43HWADHBREBH674/</a>"},{"pid":"fc0c12288c58d2aecd18564c789b4036c3712d10","tid":2225957,"uid":284432,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T16:37:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"140a0d38ee47ea54a064f0ac26bc05263b0e46ba","tid":2225957,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T16:46:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"921e83f378b1b9cf49496ba65108122400088c71","tid":2225957,"uid":378793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T16:54:31.000Z","msg":"燒死多幾件支那賤種啦"}]}